{"tid":1005512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少年下面痛仍強忍2天　開刀發現睾丸精索變扭麻花","createTime":"2019-02-02T09:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T12:40:34.000Z","uid":66271,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8daf66ad60f588d79bb3f1dc550ded241af48c","tid":1005512,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190202/photo/bkn-20190202064029571-0202_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190202091043\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190202064029571-0202_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190202091043&h=f2b23889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男士若發現私密部位出現異常，切勿因尷尬而延誤求醫，否則隨時抱憾終生。台灣高雄市一名15歲男生，日前感覺左側睾丸疼痛後，強忍2天才到醫院求醫。醫生經檢查後，證實出現「睾丸扭轉」，惟因求醫太遲，左側睾丸已發黑壞死，只能進行切除手術。<br />\n<br />\n主診醫生透露，該名少年當時由家人陪同下到醫院急診，經詢問後，少年才腼腆地表示︰「下面很痛，痛了兩天都沒好。」在為少年進行超聲波檢查及核掃描後，醫生高度懷疑少年的左側睾丸扭轉，隨即進行陰囊探查手術。<br />\n<br />\n在手術中，醫生發現少年的左側睾丸的精索，呈現如麻花式扭轉，導致睾丸在得不到足夠血流供應下壞死，只能切除。由於少年右側睾丸未來發生扭轉機會仍偏高，醫生便一併為其進行睾丸固定手術。<br />\n<br />\n主診醫生續指，雖然少年少了一顆睾丸，但其右側睾丸依具造精功能，因此不會導致不孕，惟少年術後仍感到十分沮喪。<br />\n<br />\n專家提醒，青少年睾丸因快速成長，體積與重量增加五至六倍，造成懸吊的精索與丸位置改變，較易發生睾丸扭轉；處於12至18歲青少年，如發現單側睾丸疼痛、兩側睾丸變得一高一低、陰囊腫脹等，都可能是睾丸扭轉的症狀，應把握「黃金6小時」盡速就醫。"},{"pid":"b3888646b23e96eeb05ee076e7a4f31aecded328","tid":1005512,"uid":22743,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"扭蛋"},{"pid":"d7ae6a8af457dbde1d295a5c000dcd7ccdd53c9a","tid":1005512,"uid":99473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"夾爆袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fb0e308795394d6e53e3c9a6add60a1c85cd75","tid":1005512,"uid":49366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"兩側睾丸變得一高一低<br />\n我長期都係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689de895cdea23df6b469aae65f43f01d3a5455b","tid":1005512,"uid":195348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"單丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b75feda73bd8e3c2c24531f60e9f9fa34a39781","tid":1005512,"uid":103759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"91fb0e308795394d6e53e3c9a6add60a1c85cd75","tid":1005512,"uid":49366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"兩側睾丸變得一高一低<br />\n我長期都係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"正常㗎 一樣高低會互撞 仲痛<br />\n一高一低先唔會互撞"},{"pid":"6e7d4f9f5424192190f8f4862d3f28d2ea0fef87","tid":1005512,"uid":50598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"我成日都諗 如果係古代有依啲問題可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c79fad2d5fcf23004a95be7ae61d54c142c9c83","tid":1005512,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c83cb08d482d024f11d11bbb3fd6400a42476ba","tid":1005512,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e7d4f9f5424192190f8f4862d3f28d2ea0fef87","tid":1005512,"uid":50598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"我成日都諗 如果係古代有依啲問題可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會死"},{"pid":"8b70bdbdcb1baa28a4a6393064d1feb9de6aaaf9","tid":1005512,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"單丸也是正常"},{"pid":"be497c1052d723e53ed2f5a36b631809655b347f","tid":1005512,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c83cb08d482d024f11d11bbb3fd6400a42476ba","tid":1005512,"